## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="18f90-111">다음 예제에서는 합니다 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> 작성 하는 요소 목록 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> 구 인식 포함 하는 데 사용할 수 있습니다 하는 중 하나는 국가 이름이 포함 된 요소입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="18f90-111">The following example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> element to build lists of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> elements containing country names, any one of which may be used to recognize the containing phrase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="18f90-112">이 예제에서는 다음 결과 중 하나 추가 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> 유럽 국가 및 남미 국가 대 한 각 규칙에 해당 하는 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="18f90-112">The example then adds one of the resulting <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> objects to their respective rules for European countries and South American countries.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="18f90-113">추가를 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> 개체에 대 한 그룹 규칙 참조 `ruleEurope` 및 `ruleSAmerica` 둘 중 하나는 두 가지 방법 목록으로의 음성된 입력을 인식 하는 데 사용할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="18f90-113">Further on, the example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object to group rule references to `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica` into a list of two alternatives, either one of which may be used to recognize spoken input.</span></span>  
  
```  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  
  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"),   
    new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"),   
    new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="18f90-116">다음 예제에서는 라는 문구를 인식 하는 문법의 전 세계 월드컵 성공한에 국가 이름 뒤에 "가 전 세계 월드컵에 국가".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="18f90-116">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="18f90-117">이라는 공용 규칙을 만들면 `WorldCupWinner`합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="18f90-117">It creates a public rule named `WorldCupWinner`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="18f90-118">그런 다음 두 만듭니다 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> 를 사용 하 여 개체 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> 새 배열을 포함 하는 개체 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> 개체입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="18f90-118">It then creates two <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> objects using <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> objects that contain arrays of new <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="18f90-119">이 예제에서는 발생 하는 문법을 보려면 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="18f90-119">To see the grammar that this example generates, see <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
 public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  
  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
